reviews.text: The rice bowl is very nice, the side salad is fresh. Sauces are amazing. However, the meat (lamb and chicken) is quite dry.

Food is delicious, healthy and freshly made. 
Staff are super friendly and polite.
Best freshly made Turkish kebabs!! Love the halloumi ones but hope they have fish kebabs in future, for pescatarians.
Fresh food, falafel wrap was great! Awesome vegetarian and vegan options with cheap beer!  Great spot. Some lovely environmentally friendly initiatives too! Will definitely visit again.

One of the best lamb wraps I've ever had. Apparently the falafel wraps are also amazing. Friendly service, fairly priced and has some seating available in a very central location, next to the bus stops in Sai Kung. They serve beer and have other meet and vegetarian options.

Great food and nice place. The rice was amazing we totally recommend the chicken. The salad was well prepared and the price worth it. We got the student combo and it even comes with a drink! Loved it ❤️

Muito bom! Excelente comida e o pessoal é bem gentil. Pedimos um combo de estudante que vinha com a comida e uma bebida. Salada bem temperada e arroz soltinho. Recomendo!
